snippet.title: 你们怎么选？#火影忍者 #佐助 #家庭
snippet.description:
欢迎来到【小蚂蚁】频道！🐜🌍🐂

这里是小蚂蚁依依、小宇宙浩宇和小魔王浩鸣的欢乐领地，三个性格迥异的萌娃将带领你进入他们的搞怪日常，体验充满欢笑和意想不到的冒险。😄🎈

依依，作为姐姐，古灵精怪，总能以她独特的视角发现生活中的乐趣。🐜浩宇，活泼开朗的弟弟，他的好奇心总是引领着大家探索未知的世界。🌍而浩鸣，作为家中的小魔王，调皮捣蛋却又不失可爱，总能给家庭带来满满的欢乐。🐂

在这里，你将看到这三个小宇宙的日常趣事，每一刻都充满了温暖和笑声。💖

🔔 如果你喜欢我们的视频，记得订阅并点击小铃铛图标。

请注意，本视频符合平台的使用要求，没有任何违规行为。

我们的视频制作团队会特别关注儿童的安全需求，确保内容不会对其造成任何危害。

snippet.title: Toddler stops crying when she receives cash
snippet.description:
A toddler who was having a tantrum only stopped when she received a banknote.

Two-year-old Precious Marlette Asid was crying as she wanted to be with her father who went to work in Cavite, the Philippines, on November 18.

Her mother, Brigitte Balneg, tried distracting her with snacks and toys, but to no avail. But when she was given a 1,000 PHP (14 GBP) bill, the little girl ceased sobbing.

Footage shows Precious Marlette being given candy and juice amid her favourite toys.

When mum Brigitte showed her the money, the kid stopped instantly.

Brigitte said: 'She kept chasing after her daddy, and she did not want everything I gave.

'I was not really expecting my baby's reaction since it was her first time seeing bills. I do not usually let her handle money, especially coins.

She probably thought it was a new toy because it was something new to her. Well, my child is only two-years-old, and she does not understand money yet, and I have never introduced her to it.'

(1 PHP=0.014 GBP)

If you love katana unboxing, then you'll love this. See the Katanas slice in action as satisfying as ASMR! These aren't rusted katanas! Sword-making, blacksmithing, knife making, and katana making are Mini Katana's passions! If you love anime like One Piece, Naruto, Demon Slayer, Attack on Titan, Miira No Kaikata, Mugen Train, Jujutsu Kaisen, sword art online abridged, slice of life anime, chainsaw man vs katana, afro samurai and are excited about the Swordsmith arc, you're gonna love our ninja weapons! Mini Katana is the founding titan of katana making, knife making, and the mini katana keychain. Learn how to draw a katana and how to make kunai like Naruto. We are the last samurai. We love Japanese anime, Japanese history, Japanese lofi, Japanese movies, and Japanese songs. Subscribe to watch mini katana unboxing, how to make a katana with cardboard and with paper, and more!  The Mini Katana Store is committed to high quality carbon steel blades and giving you slice of life looks as we try not to laugh challenge.
